@*@model其實是@ViewData.Model*@
@*Model => Controller:ViewData.Model => View*@
@*@model namespace.className*@

@*Q1:@Model != @model?
Q2:為何沒有引入model，也能使用@Model.id?   A:
Q3:Controller也沒有指定ViewData.Model為data，只有return View(data)，那@Model.id怎麼來的?*@


<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title></title>
</head>
<body>
    <form style="margin-left:10px;">
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="exampleInputEmail1">學號</label>
            <input type="text" id="exampleInputEmail1" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Enter email" value="@Model.id">
            <small id="emailHelp">請輸入數字</small>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="exampleInputPassword1">姓名</label>
            <input type="text" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="Password" value="@ViewData.Model.name">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="exampleInputEmail1">分數</label>
            <input type="text" id="exampleInputEmail1" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Enter email" value="@ViewData.Model.score ">
        </div>
        <button type="submit">確定</button>
    </form>
</body>
</html>
